{
  "stem": "17374.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 291.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what you asked me before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was before the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a beautiful day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was summer, as I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I opened my eyes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw the boys start to look at me, and, and it was one Polish boy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- he was son of the-- how you call it?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Master or major of the [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[POLISH] is a word I don't know how you say in English.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was tall, and blond, and blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was not a Jewish family who lived there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were some Jews who live in, in that county.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was five brother, and the older ones was Romek, and he was in love with me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was top of the world that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was most best time in my life, I might say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a war was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but I didn't know much about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a few months only.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe I was already 17, because '39 was still-- 16 and 1/2, nearly 17.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was very strong girl, and I was flirt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I got flowers, and I got-- it was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we [INAUDIBLE] ordered to-- we have to leave this and go much further to the country, not so close to the [INAUDIBLE] or ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First time we heard that ghetto is starting to be built, ghetto, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is ghetto?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my sister already knew, and she decided, instead of going to the country, we should go to ghetto, be with Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When was the first time you heard about the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was, well, after when we went Tonie, I think eight months or something like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we find out that we have to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
